title: Adorable kittens are in perfect harmony in cute video
text: Share this article Share The curious kittens are perched on a wooden stand as they perform their accidental dance routine. The short clip was shared on Instagram and is backed by a playful song. Posted on the social media site two weeks ago the video has already had nearly 20,000 views. It was posted by Instagram user oje3423 who has 21,000 follows - maybe because the feed is exclusively pictures of cute cats. It isn't clear where it was filmed. In a super cute clip the felines are seen moving in complete syncronisation with each other Share or comment on this article Most watched News videos
